From 724293096d92f6e9dda8730507dcaefc6e349bae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Jochen=20Sch=C3=A4fer?= <josch1710@live.de>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 08:03:54 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] Port to Macos

1. Macos needs some essentials defines in sys/types.h

2. ar doesn't need -o, breaks on Macos

3. Arm target doesn't compile int, so we use builtin trap

4. Implemented _execname
---
